OL,6,FTwo men have been convicted after a
OL,7,Ffather of two was beaten to death in .
OL,9,FAli Salih Abdalaah, 36, died after he
OL,10,Fwas attacked in a hallway in Brecon
OL,11,FTower, Guild Close, in in October 2022.
OL,13,FAfter a three week trial at , Dale
OL,14,FBerry-Parkes, 32, from Birmingham, has
OL,15,Fbeen convicted of manslaughter.
OL,17,FA second man, Hardi Hamad, 35, also
OL,18,Ffrom Birmingham, pleaded guilty to
OL,19,Fmanslaughter with diminished
OL,20,Fresponsibility during the trial.
