OL,6,FJust after 6am on 8 October 2022 Ali
OL,7,FSalih Abdalaah visited on a shop on
OL,8,FSoho Road before meeting a woman who
OL,9,Fhe took back to his flat.
OL,11,FAround 9am, the woman called Hardi
OL,12,FHamad and Dale Berry-Parkes, claiming
OL,13,Fshe had been sexually assaulted.
OL,15,FThe two men then turned up outside Ali
OL,16,FSalih Abdalaah's front door and
OL,17,Ffatally attacked him on his doorstep.
OL,19,FCCTV footage then shows Berry-Parkes
OL,20,Fthrowing a set of car keys to Hamad,
OL,21,Fwhich belonged to Ali's red Kia.
