OL,6,FThe two men then drove off in convoy
OL,7,Fin Ali's stolen vehicle and the
OL,8,FPeugeot they had arrived in.
OL,10,FSeveral days later, both of the cars
OL,11,Fwere recovered with false plates.
OL,13,FOn 12 October, after handing
OL,14,Fthemselves in to a police station,
OL,15,FHamad and Berry-Parkes were arrested.
OL,17,FThey are due to be sentenced at
OL,18,FBirmingham Crown Court at a later date.
