OL,6,FIn tribute to Ali, his family said:
OL,7,F"Ali was a very hard working, happy
OL,8,Fand kind man.
OL,10,F"He was a loving father who dedicated
OL,11,Fhis life to his children. He loved to
OL,12,Fwork within the community,
OL,13,Fvolunteering to help those less
OL,14,Ffortunate than himself.
OL,16,F"Our lives have been shattered. As a
OL,17,Ffamily and community particularly his
OL,18,Fyoung children, we are all devastated
OL,19,Fby his death which has changed our
OL,20,Fchildren's lives forever."
