OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Laura
OL,7,FHarrison, from our Homicide Unit,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Two children have been left
OL,9,Fwithout a father due to the appalling
OL,10,Factions of Hamad and Berry-Parkes.
OL,12,F"The men launched a horrific senseless
OL,13,Fattack on Mr Abdalaah on the doorstep
OL,14,Fof his home.
OL,16,F"I hope this conviction brings some
OL,17,Fclosure to Ali's family following
OL,18,Ftheir tragic loss. Our thoughts remain
OL,19,Fwith them."
